    "The effect of the node structures in the UNet??",
    "structure on the success was also examined in the study.",
    "As a result of this examination, it has been seen that the high number of nodes in the same layer can negatively affect both the success and the process cost.",
    "For this reason, an attention module has been proposed in the study, similar to the node structure used in UNet?",
    "?, but with different content.The proposed attention module has three inputs and one output, as shown in Fig. 4."
